Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:43.63,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}別來煩擾我  Craze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:48.97,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}堅持自我  即使四面楚歌  yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:51.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}身處起點時就已危機四伏
